ted solution offers clients an industryleading user experience to manage absence leave and disability and includes more than  us federal state and municipal leave policies in addition to the ability to add organizationspecific leave policies such as personal medical and paid family leaves this helps organizations improve efficiencies and demonstrate compliance in a report on trends in human resources morneau shepell found that  per cent of employers do not track the cost of casual and incidental absence to help solve this issue morneau shepell provides a unique fully integrated approach to managing absence leave and disability which includes comprehensive day one notification option the system fully supports realtime absence notification from all causes as well as the ability to track various banks of time such as paid time off paid family leave sick and safe time off vacation and numerous other items in a single place recognizing the need to provide innovative tools to better engage employees and employers abiliti™absence is accessible around the clock to notify and track absences from work through a mobile app interactive voice response call center and web portal abiliti™absences powerful dashboarding delivers realtime reporting analytics and improves overall management of absence leave and disability we are pleased to partner with presagia as it is the industrys most trusted source of knowledge and technology for leave management compliance said zahid salman executive vice president morneau shepell by incorporating presagias compliance engine into morneau shepells abiliti™absence technology platform we are able to now provide the same level of industry leading absence management solutions in the united states that we currently provide in canada this solution is currently available for demonstration for more information on morneau shepells abiliti™absence solution visit morneaushepellcom about morneau shepell morneau shepell is the only human resources consulting 